title: Mountain Ocean Skin Trip Moisturizer, Coconut, 8-Ounce
description: The extremely fast absorbing and unique moisturizing properties of Skin Trip come from active ingredietns, coconut oil, aloe vera and distilled lanolin. This product is made in small batches to ensure the highest quality and freshness. Skin Trip is a delicately balanced blend that is at is best when fresh. Keep from freezing and high heat. Everybody's favorite skin moisturizer has been blended by the same family owned company since 1971. Skin Trip's unique light smooth feel is perfect after sun, after shower, after shave, anytime. No animal testing.
